description.en:
What is the project about?
About Getting $REKT

What makes your project unique?
The utility is $REKT

History of your project.
I made a poll on Twitter if my followers want to get rekted by buying a token called $REKT (https://twitter.com/rektfencer/status/1648683479343808512). Having received a positive response from them, I began to develop the project.

What’s next for your project?
CEX listings, NFT collection, Staking 

What can your token be used for?
To get REKTed (and soon for staking)
